                            <comment id="17110735" author="dcapwell" created="Tue, 19 May 2020 00:56:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seeing how this feature was added to 4.0, we should not release with this bug; so marked it for beta.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17110743" author="dcapwell" created="Tue, 19 May 2020 00:57:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its possible the defaults for the cluster are set to false, so absence of --blocking would be non-blocking, but in the cases where the configs are true and you  should still be able to mark non-blocking.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
